  <p>
    The ISJ annual Art Exhibition was a vibrant display of imagination and skill from pupils across the school. Each piece told a unique story, reflecting the creative development encouraged throughout the curriculum.
  </p>

  <p>
    Families and staff gathered to celebrate the work on display, which spanned drawing, painting, sculpture, and mixed media from Early Years through to the senior year groups. The exhibition is a highlight of the school calendar and a testament to the role that the arts play in every child's education at ISJ.
  </p>

